com.igeekinc.indelible.indeliblefs.iscsi

Class IndelibleFSTargetConfigurationXMLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jscsi.target.settings.TargetConfigurationXMLParser
      • com.igeekinc.indelible.indeliblefs.iscsi.IndelibleFSTargetConfigurationXMLParser

  • public class IndelibleFSTargetConfigurationXMLParser
extends org.jscsi.target.settings.TargetConfigurationXMLParser
    Instances of TargetConfiguration provides access target-wide parameters, variables that are the same across all sessions and connections that do not change after initialization and which play a role during text parameter negotiation. Some of these parameters are provided or can be overridden by the content of an XML file - jscsi-target.xml.
    Author:
    Andreas Ergenzinger
